						<p>Slab set up in a field called ‘Beḍagalkaṭṭe hola’.</p>						

						<p>Sōyidēva.</p>						

						<p>The badly damaged record registers a gift of land in the villages Uppugunda and Hesarūru to Nāraṇa-kāraṁtaḍigaḷu. All other details are lost.</p>						

